  ğŸ”’ SECURITY & MONITORING

  Enterprise Security Architecture:

  Security Implementation:
  â”œâ”€â”€ Network Security:
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ VPC isolation (private subnets)
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Security groups with minimal open ports
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ WAF protection (AWS WAF/CloudFlare)
  â”‚   â””â”€â”€ DDoS protection (Shield Advanced)
  â”œâ”€â”€ Application Security:
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ API key management (AWS Secrets Manager)
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ SSL/TLS encryption (Certificate Manager)
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Authentication (OAuth 2.0 + OpenID Connect)
  â”‚   â””â”€â”€ Authorization (RBAC with fine-grained permissions)
  â”œâ”€â”€ Data Security:
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Encryption at rest (S3 SSE-S3)
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Encryption in transit (TLS 1.3)
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Database encryption (RDS encryption)
  â”‚   â””â”€â”€ Backup encryption (cross-account KMS)
  â””â”€â”€ Monitoring Security:
      â”œâ”€â”€ CloudTrail for audit logging
      â”œâ”€â”€ GuardDuty for threat detection
      â”œâ”€â”€ Security Hub for compliance
      â””â”€â”€ Custom security monitoring

  Monitoring & Observability:

  Monitoring Stack:
  â”œâ”€â”€ Infrastructure Monitoring:
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ CloudWatch / Stackdriver
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Prometheus + Grafana
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ DataDog (optional)
  â”‚   â””â”€â”€ Custom health checks
  â”œâ”€â”€ Application Monitoring:
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ APM (Application Performance Monitoring)
  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Error tracking (Sentry)
